      "role": "user",
      "content": "i used to feel everything through the brush... like there was this constant hum of color and meaning behind my eyes. but lately, it's just gone. i look at the canvas and i feel nothing. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back. it's like the part of me that actually lived just... evaporated. now im just this hollow shell walking around, just going through the motions. i feel so empty.",
