    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "what do you mean \"stop carrying a ghost\"? it just feels like i'm wasting space. like i'm just a biological machine that's still running even though the pilot left the cockpit. if the essence of who i was is actually gone, what is even the point of the rest of it?",
