    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i dont want to find something new. i don't want to start over. that sounds so exhausting. what if there's nothing left to build with? if the machine is just running on autopilot without the soul, it doesn't feel like \"something new,\" it just feels like a heavy, pointless weight. it feels like i'm just waiting for the battery to die anyway.",
